    <item>
      <title>德国将加快国防工业重组中的武器采购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/germany-to-speed-up-arms-purchases-in-defense-industry-shake-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国计划加快武器采购审批，并为大型武器合同提供更多规划确定性，以推动俄罗斯入侵乌克兰后调整其国防工业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/germany-to-speed-up-arms-purchases-in-defense-industry-shake-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 18:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非国民议会支持征用法案草案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/south-africa-s-national-assembly-backs-draft-expropriation-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非执政党非洲人国民大会的立法者投票支持新起草的立法，该立法将允许政府为了国家利益而无偿征用土地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/south-africa-s-national-assembly-backs-draft-expropriation-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:13:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦警告中国工业增长正在扭曲世界经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/yellen-sounds-alarm-on-china-roiling-world-with-industry-ramp-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦(Janet Yellen)抨击中国利用补贴为关键新兴行业的制造商提供竞争优势，但代价是扭曲全球经济，并表示她计划在即将到来的访问中就这一问题向中国施压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/yellen-sounds-alarm-on-china-roiling-world-with-industry-ramp-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:49:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
